WEBVTT

00:01:28.266 --> 00:01:30.646
to tear down his wall.

00:01:31.924 --> 00:01:34.714
You're a conservative member of Congress,

00:01:34.738 --> 00:01:37.656
and you agree with President
John F. Kennedy

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:40.262
that America is an exceptional place.

00:01:41.287 --> 00:01:42.915
For inspiration,

00:01:42.939 --> 00:01:47.060
you go to YouTube and you watch
his speech at Rice University,

00:01:47.084 --> 00:01:49.553
September of 1962,

00:01:49.577 --> 00:01:51.002
the "moon shot" speech.

00:01:51.896 --> 00:01:56.039
And you're amazed
that he admits in that speech --

00:01:56.063 --> 00:02:00.293
a speech of 17 minutes of pure
American exceptionalism --